#: cms/templates/index.html:538 cms/templates/index.html:546
msgid "Create Your First Library"
msgstr "Opret dit første bibliotek"

#: cms/templates/index.html:540
msgid ""
"Libraries hold a pool of components that can be re-used across multiple "
"courses. Create your first library with the click of a button!"
msgstr ""
"Biblioteker indeholder en pulje af komponenter, som kan genbruges på tværs "
"af flere kurser. Opret dit første bibliotek med et enkelt klik!"

#: cms/templates/index.html:557
#, python-brace-format
msgid "New to {studio_name}?"
msgstr "Ny hos {studio_name}?"

#: cms/templates/index.html:558
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Click Help in the upper-right corner to get more information about the "
"{studio_name} page you are viewing. You can also use the links at the bottom"
" of the page to access our continually updated documentation and other "
"{studio_name} resources."
msgstr ""
"Klik på Hjælp i øverste højre hjørne for at få flere oplysninger om den "
"{studio_name}-side, du ser. Du kan også bruge linkene nederst på siden for "
"at få adgang til vores løbende opdaterede dokumentation og andre "
"{studio_name}-ressourcer."

#: cms/templates/index.html:563
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Getting Started with {studio_name}"
msgstr "Kom godt i gang med {studio_name}"

#: cms/templates/index.html:570 cms/templates/index.html:582
#: cms/templates/index.html:588
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Can I create courses in {studio_name}?"
msgstr "Kan jeg oprette kurser i {studio_name}?"

#: cms/templates/index.html:571
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"In order to create courses in {studio_name}, you must {link_start}contact "
"{platform_name} staff to help you create a course{link_end}."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette kurser i {studio_name} skal du {link_start}kontakte "
"{platform_name} medarbejdere for at få hjælp til at oprette et "
"kursus{link_end}."

#: cms/templates/index.html:583
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"In order to create courses in {studio_name}, you must have course creator "
"privileges to create your own course."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette kurser i {studio_name} skal du have rettigheder til at "
"oprette kurser, så du kan oprette dit eget kursus."

#: cms/templates/index.html:589
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Your request to author courses in {studio_name} has been denied. Please "
"{link_start}contact {platform_name} Staff with further questions{link_end}."
msgstr ""
"Din anmodning om at udarbejde kurser i {studio_name} er blevet afvist. "
"{link_start}Kontakt {platform_name} medarbejdere{link_end} ved yderligere "
"spørgsmål."

#: cms/templates/index.html:606
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Thanks for signing up, {name}!"
msgstr "Tak for tilmeldingen, {name}!"

#: cms/templates/index.html:611
msgid "We need to verify your email address"
msgstr "Vi skal bekræfte din e-mailadresse"

#: cms/templates/index.html:613
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Almost there! In order to complete your sign up we need you to verify your "
"email address ({email}). An activation message and next steps should be "
"waiting for you there."
msgstr ""
"Næsten færdig! For at fuldføre din tilmelding skal du bekræfte din "
"e-mailadresse ({email}). En aktiveringsbesked og videre instruktioner venter"
" på dig."

#: cms/templates/index.html:621
msgid "Need help?"
msgstr "Brug for hjælp?"

#: cms/templates/index.html:622
msgid ""
"Please check your Junk or Spam folders in case our email isn't in your "
"INBOX. Still can't find the verification email? Request help via the link "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Tjek venligst dine mapper for uønsket post eller spam, hvis vores e-mail "
"ikke er i din INBOX. Kan du stadig ikke finde bekræftelses-e-mailen? Anmod "
"om hjælp via linket nedenfor."

#: cms/templates/library-block-author-preview-header.html:8
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Showing all matching content eligible to be added into {display_name}. Each "
"student will be assigned {max_count} component drawn randomly from this "
"list."
msgid_plural ""
"Showing all matching content eligible to be added into {display_name}. Each "
"student will be assigned {max_count} components drawn randomly from this "
"list."
msgstr[0] ""
"Viser alt matchende indhold, der er berettiget til at blive tilføjet til "
"{display_name}. Hver elev vil blive tildelt {max_count} komponent udvalgt "
"tilfældigt fra denne liste."
msgstr[1] ""
"Viser alt matchende indhold, der er berettiget til at blive tilføjet til "
"{display_name}. Hver elev vil blive tildelt {max_count} komponenter udvalgt "
"tilfældigt fra denne liste."

#: cms/templates/library.html:49
msgid "Content Library"
msgstr "Indholdsbibliotek"

#: cms/templates/library.html:61
msgid "Add Component"
msgstr "Tilføj komponent"

#: cms/templates/library.html:90
msgid "Adding content to your library"
msgstr "Tilføjer indhold til dit bibliotek"

#: cms/templates/library.html:91
msgid ""
"Add components to your library for use in courses, using Add New Component "
"at the bottom of this page."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj komponenter til dit bibliotek til brug i kurser, ved at bruge 'Tilføj"
" ny komponent' nederst på siden."

#: cms/templates/library.html:92
msgid ""
"Components are listed in the order in which they are added, with the most "
"recently added at the bottom. Use the pagination arrows to navigate from "
"page to page if you have more than one page of components in your library."
msgstr ""
"Komponenterne vises i den rækkefølge, de er tilføjet, med de nyeste nederst."
" Brug pagineringspile for at navigere mellem sider, hvis du har mere end én "
"side med komponenter i dit bibliotek."

#: cms/templates/library.html:93
msgid "Using library content in courses"
msgstr "Brug af biblioteksindhold i kurser"

#: cms/templates/library.html:94
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Use library content in courses by adding the "
"{em_start}library_content{em_end} policy key to the Advanced Module List in "
"the course's Advanced Settings, then adding a Randomized Content Block to "
"your courseware. In the settings for each Randomized Content Block, select "
"this library as the source library, and specify the number of problems to be"
" randomly selected and displayed to each student."
msgstr ""
"Brug biblioteksindhold i kurser ved at tilføje policy-nøglen "
"{em_start}library_content{em_end} til den avancerede modul liste i kursets "
"avancerede indstillinger, og derefter tilføje en tilfældigt sorteret "
"indholdsblok til dit kursusmateriale. I indstillingerne for hver tilfældigt "
"sorteret indholdsblok, vælg dette bibliotek som kildebibliotek, og angiv "
"antallet af opgaver, der tilfældigt skal vælges og vises for hver "
"studerende."

#: cms/templates/library.html:101
msgid "Learn more about content libraries"
msgstr "Lær mere om indholdsbiblioteker"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:12
msgid "Course Team Settings"
msgstr "Kursusteamindstillinger"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:36 cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:37
msgid "New Team Member"
msgstr "Nyt teammedlem"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:51
msgid "Add a User to Your Course's Team"
msgstr "Tilføj en bruger til dit kursusteam"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:54 cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:55
msgid "New Team Member Information"
msgstr "Oplysninger om nyt teammedlem"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:58 cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:59
msgid "User's Email Address"
msgstr "Brugerens e-mailadresse"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:59 cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:60
#: themes/stanford-style/lms/templates/register-form.html:84
#: themes/stanford-style/lms/templates/register-form.html:128
#: themes/stanford-style/lms/templates/register-shib.html:135
msgid "example: username@domain.com"
msgstr "F. eks.: brugernavn@domæne.dk"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:60
msgid "Provide the email address of the user you want to add as Staff"
msgstr "Angiv e-mailadressen for den bruger, du vil tilføje som medarbejder"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:67 cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:68
msgid "Add User"
msgstr "Tilføj bruger"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:83
msgid "Add Team Members to This Course"
msgstr "Tilføj teammedlemmer til dette kursus"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:85
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Adding team members makes course authoring collaborative. Users must be "
"signed up for {studio_name} and have an active account."
msgstr ""
"Tilføjelse af teammedlemmer gør kursusudarbejdelsen samarbejdende. Brugere "
"skal være tilmeldt {studio_name} og have en aktiv konto."

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:91
msgid "Add a New Team Member"
msgstr "Tilføj et nyt teammedlem"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:100
msgid "Course Team Roles"
msgstr "Roller i kurseteamet"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:101
msgid ""
"Course team members with the Staff role are course co-authors. They have "
"full writing and editing privileges on all course content."
msgstr ""
"Medlemmer af kurseteamet med rollen Medarbejder er medforfattere til kurset."
" De har fulde skrive- og redigeringsrettigheder til alt kursusindhold."

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:103
msgid ""
"Admins are course team members who can add and remove other course team "
"members."
msgstr ""
"Administratorer er medlemmer af kurseteamet, som kan tilføje og fjerne andre"
" teammedlemmer."

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:104
msgid ""
"All course team members can access content in Studio, the LMS, and Insights,"
" and they are automatically enrolled in the course."
msgstr ""
"Alle medlemmer af kurseteamet kan få adgang til indhold i Studio, LMS og "
"Insights, og de tilmeldes automatisk kurset."

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:109
msgid "Transferring Ownership"
msgstr "Overdragelse af ejerskab"

#: cms/templates/manage_users.html:111
msgid ""
"Every course must have an Admin. If you are the Admin and you want to "
"transfer ownership of the course, click <strong>Add admin access</strong> to"
" make another user the Admin, then ask that user to remove you from the "
"Course Team list."
msgstr ""
"Hvert kursus skal have en administrator. Hvis du er administrator og ønsker "
"at overdrage ejerskabet af kurset, skal du klikke på <strong>Tilføj "
"administratoradgang</strong> for at gøre en anden bruger til administrator, "
"og derefter bede den bruger om at fjerne dig fra kursusteamet."

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:13
msgid "Library User Access"
msgstr "Biblioteksbrugeradgang"

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:29
#: cms/templates/widgets/header.html:302
msgid "User Access"
msgstr "Brugeradgang"

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:52
msgid "Grant Access to This Library"
msgstr "Giv adgang til dette bibliotek"

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:61
msgid "Provide the email address of the user you want to add"
msgstr "Angiv e-mailadressen for den bruger, du vil tilføje"

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:84
msgid "Add More Users to This Library"
msgstr "Tilføj flere brugere til dette bibliotek"

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:86
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Grant other members of your course team access to this library. New library "
"users must have an active {studio_name} account."
msgstr ""
"Giv andre medlemmer af dit kursusteam adgang til dette bibliotek. Nye "
"biblioteksbrugere skal have en aktiv {studio_name}-konto."

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:92
msgid "Add a New User"
msgstr "Tilføj en ny bruger"

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:101
msgid "Library Access Roles"
msgstr "Biblioteksadgangsroller"

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:102
msgid "There are three access roles for libraries: User, Staff, and Admin."
msgstr ""
"Der er tre adgangsroller for biblioteker: Bruger, Medarbejder og "
"Administrator."

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:103
msgid ""
"Library Users can view library content and can reference or use library "
"components in their courses, but they cannot edit the contents of a library."
msgstr ""
"Biblioteksbrugere kan se biblioteksindhold og referere til eller bruge "
"biblioteks-komponenter i deres kurser, men de kan ikke redigere indholdet i "
"et bibliotek."

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:104
msgid ""
"Library Staff are content co-authors. They have full editing privileges on "
"the contents of a library."
msgstr ""
"Biblioteksmedarbejdere er medforfattere til indholdet. De har fulde "
"redigeringsrettigheder til et biblioteks indhold."

#: cms/templates/manage_users_lib.html:105
msgid ""
"Library Admins have full editing privileges and can also add and remove "
"other team members. There must be at least one user with the Admin role in a"
" library."
msgstr ""
"Biblioteksadministratorer har fulde redigeringsrettigheder og kan også "
"tilføje og fjerne andre teammedlemmer. Der skal være mindst én bruger med "
"administratorrollen i et bibliotek."

