msgstr "Kursusoversigtsside"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:92
msgid "(for student enrollment and access)"
msgstr "(til studietilmelding og adgang)"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:103
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Enroll in {course_display_name}"
msgstr "Tilmeld dig {course_display_name}"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:106
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The course \"{course_display_name}\", provided by {platform_name}, is open "
"for enrollment. Please navigate to this course at {link_for_about_page} to "
"enroll."
msgstr ""
"Kurset \"{course_display_name}\", udbydes af {platform_name}, er åbent for "
"tilmelding. Naviger venligst til dette kursus via {link_for_about_page} for "
"at tilmelde dig."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:112
msgid "Send a note to students via email"
msgstr "Send en besked til de studerende via e-mail"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:114
msgid "Invite your students"
msgstr "Inviter dine studerende"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:122
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Promoting Your Course with {platform_name}"
msgstr "Promover dit kursus med {platform_name}"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:125
msgid ""
"Your course summary page will not be viewable until your course has been "
"announced. To provide content for the page and preview it, follow the "
"instructions provided by your Program Manager."
msgstr ""
"Din kursusoversigtsside vil ikke være synlig, før dit kursus er blevet "
"offentliggjort. For at tilføje indhold til siden og se en forhåndsvisning, "
"følg vejledningen fra din programchef."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:129
msgid ""
"Please note that changes here may take up to a business day to appear on "
"your course summary page."
msgstr ""
"Bemærk, at ændringer her kan tage op til en arbejdsdag, før de vises på din "
"kursusoversigtsside."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:141
msgid "Course Credit Requirements"
msgstr "Kursuskrav for studiepoint"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:142
msgid "Steps required to earn course credit"
msgstr "Trin, der kræves for at opnå kursuspoint"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:150 cms/templates/settings.html:152
msgid "Minimum Grade"
msgstr "Minimumskarakter"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:161
msgid "Successful Proctored Exam"
msgstr "Bestået overvåget eksamen"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:163
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Proctored Exam {number}"
msgstr "Overvåget eksamen {number}"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:172
msgid "ID Verification"
msgstr "ID-verifikation"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:174
#, python-brace-format
msgid "In-Course Reverification {number}"
msgstr "Genbekræftelse under kurset {number}"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:192
msgid "Course Pacing"
msgstr "Kursus tempo"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:193
msgid "Set the pacing for this course"
msgstr "Indstil tempoet for dette kursus"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:201
msgid "Instructor-Paced"
msgstr "Instruktørstyret"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:202
msgid ""
"Instructor-paced courses progress at the pace that the course author sets. "
"You can configure release dates for course content and due dates for "
"assignments."
msgstr ""
"Instruktørstyrede kurser forløber i det tempo, kursusforfatteren sætter. Du "
"kan konfigurere frigivelsesdatoer for kursusindhold og afleveringsdatoer for"
" opgaver."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:206
msgid "Self-Paced"
msgstr "Selvstyret"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:207
msgid ""
"Self-paced courses offer suggested due dates for assignments or exams based "
"on the learner’s enrollment date and the expected course duration. These "
"courses offer learners flexibility to modify the assignment dates as needed."
msgstr ""
"Selvstyrede kurser tilbyder foreslåede afleveringsdatoer for opgaver eller "
"eksamener baseret på den studerendes tilmeldingsdato og den forventede "
"kursusvarighed. Disse kurser giver de studerende fleksibilitet til at ændre "
"afleveringsdatoerne efter behov."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:217
msgid "Course Schedule"
msgstr "Kursusplan"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:218
msgid "Dates that control when your course can be viewed"
msgstr "Datoer, der styrer, hvornår dit kursus kan ses"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:224
msgid "Course Start Date"
msgstr "Kursusstartdato"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:227
msgid "First day the course begins"
msgstr "Første dag, hvor kurset begynder"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:231
msgid "Course Start Time"
msgstr "Kursusstarttidspunkt"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:233 cms/templates/settings.html:248
#: cms/templates/settings.html:312 cms/templates/settings.html:335
#: cms/templates/settings.html:355
msgid "(UTC)"
msgstr "(UTC)"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:239
msgid "Course End Date"
msgstr "Kursusafslutningsdato"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:242
msgid "Last day your course is active"
msgstr "Sidste dag, hvor dit kursus er aktivt"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:246
msgid "Course End Time"
msgstr "Kursusafslutningstidspunkt"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:259 cms/templates/settings.html:276
msgid "Immediately upon passing"
msgstr "Så snart bestået"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:260
msgid "End date of course"
msgstr "Kursusafslutningsdato"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:261 cms/templates/settings.html:284
msgid "A date after the course end date"
msgstr "En dato efter kursusafslutningsdatoen"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:263
msgid "Certificates are awarded at the end of a course run"
msgstr "Certifikater uddeles ved afslutningen af et kursusforløb"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:270
msgid "Read more about this setting"
msgstr "Læs mere om denne indstilling"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:274
msgid ""
"In all configurations of this setting, certificates are generated for "
"learners as soon as they achieve the passing threshold in the course (which "
"can occur before a final assignment based on course design)"
msgstr ""
"I alle konfigurationer af denne indstilling genereres certifikater til de "
"studerende, så snart de opnår den beståelsesgrænse, der er fastsat for "
"kurset (hvilket kan ske før en afsluttende opgave, afhængigt af "
"kursusdesignet)"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:277
msgid ""
"Learners can access their certificate as soon as they achieve a passing "
"grade above the course grade threshold. Note: learners can achieve a passing"
" grade before encountering all assignments in some course configurations."
msgstr ""
"De studerende kan få adgang til deres certifikat, så snart de opnår en "
"bestået karakter over den fastsatte grænse for kurset. Bemærk: I nogle "
"kursuskonfigurationer kan de studerende opnå en bestået karakter, før de har"
" gennemført alle opgaver."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:280
msgid "On course end date"
msgstr "På kursusafslutningsdatoen"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:281
msgid ""
"Learners with passing grades can access their certificate once the end date "
"of the course has elapsed."
msgstr ""
"Studerende med bestået karakter kan få adgang til deres certifikat, når "
"kursusafslutningsdatoen er passeret."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:285
msgid ""
"Learners with passing grades can access their certificate after the date "
"that you set has elapsed."
msgstr ""
"Studerende med bestået karakter kan få adgang til deres certifikat, efter "
"den dato, du har fastsat, er passeret."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:292
msgid "Certificates Available Date"
msgstr "Dato for certifikattilgængelighed"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:303
msgid "Enrollment Start Date"
msgstr "Tilmeldingsstartdato"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:306
msgid "First day students can enroll"
msgstr "Første dag, de studerende kan tilmelde sig"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:310
msgid "Enrollment Start Time"
msgstr "Tilmeldingsstarttidspunkt"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:321
msgid "Enrollment End Date"
msgstr "Tilmeldingsslutdato"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:325
msgid "Last day students can enroll."
msgstr "Sidste dag, de studerende kan tilmelde sig."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:327 cms/templates/settings.html:348
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Contact your {platform_name} partner manager to update these settings."
msgstr ""
"Kontakt din {platform_name} partneransvarlige for at opdatere disse "
"indstillinger."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:333
msgid "Enrollment End Time"
msgstr "Tilmeldingssluttidspunkt"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:344
msgid "Upgrade Deadline Date"
msgstr "Opgraderingsfristens dato"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:347
msgid "Last day students can upgrade to a verified enrollment."
msgstr ""
"Sidste dag, de studerende kan opgradere til en verificeret tilmelding."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:353
msgid "Upgrade Deadline Time"
msgstr "Opgraderingsfristens tid"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:365
msgid "Course Details"
msgstr "Kursusdetaljer"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:366
msgid "Provide useful information about your course"
msgstr "Angiv nyttige oplysninger om dit kursus"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:377
msgid ""
"Identify the course language here. This is used to assist users find courses"
" that are taught in a specific language. It is also used to localize the "
"'From:' field in bulk emails."
msgstr ""
"Angiv her kursets sprog. Dette bruges til at hjælpe brugere med at finde "
"kurser, der undervises på et bestemt sprog. Det bruges også til at "
"lokalisere 'Fra:' feltet i masse-e-mails."

#: cms/templates/settings.html:388
msgid "Introducing Your Course"
msgstr "Introduktion til dit kursus"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:389
msgid "Information for prospective students"
msgstr "Oplysninger til potentielle studerende"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:397
msgid "Course Title"
msgstr "Kurstitel"

#: cms/templates/settings.html:399
msgid "Displayed as title on the course details page. Limit to 50 characters."
