#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:11
#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:101
msgid ""
"Enter email addresses and/or usernames separated by new lines or commas."
msgstr ""
"Angiv email-adresser og/eller brugernavne, adskilt linjeskift eller kommaer."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:12
msgid ""
"You will not get notification for emails that bounce, so please double-check"
" spelling."
msgstr ""
"Du vil ikke få besked om emails som ikke går igennem, så dobbel-tjek "
"venligst stavningen."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:18
msgid ""
"Enter the reason why the students are to be manually enrolled or unenrolled."
msgstr ""
"Notér årsagen til at kursisterne skal tilmeldes eller frameldes manuelt."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:19
msgid ""
"This cannot be left blank and will be recorded and presented in Enrollment "
"Reports."
msgstr ""
"Dette felt kan ikke være tomt og vil blive medtaget og vist i "
"TilmeldingsRapporterne"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:20
msgid "Therefore, please give enough detail to account for this action."
msgstr ""
"Derfor bedes du give detaljer nok til at tage højde for denne handling."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:21
#: lms/templates/support/feature_based_enrollments.html:41
#: lms/templates/support/feature_based_enrollments.html:44
msgid "Reason"
msgstr "Årsag"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:64
msgid "Register/Enroll Students"
msgstr "Registrer/Tilmeld Kursister"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:65
msgid ""
"To register and enroll a list of users in this course, choose a CSV file "
"that contains the following columns in this exact order: email, username, "
"name, and country. Please include one student per row and do not include any"
" headers, footers, or blank lines. Optionally, extra columns can be "
"provided: cohort and course mode, in that order. These extra columns may be "
"blank."
msgstr ""
"For at registrere og tilmelde en liste over brugere på dette kursus skal du "
"vælge en CSV-fil, der indeholder følgende kolonner i nøjagtig denne "
"rækkefølge: e-mail, brugernavn, navn og land. Inkluder venligst én elev pr. "
"række og medtag ikke overskrifter, sidefødder eller tomme linjer. Valgfrit "
"kan der angives ekstra kolonner: kohorte- og kursustilstand i nævnte "
"rækkefølge. Disse ekstra kolonner kan være tomme."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:68
msgid "Upload a CSV for bulk enrollment"
msgstr "Upload en CSV til massetilmelding"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:75
msgid "Upload CSV"
msgstr "Upload CSV"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:99
msgid "Batch Beta Tester Addition"
msgstr "Batch Beta Tester Tilføjelse"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:102
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Note: Users must have an activated {platform_name} account before they can "
"be enrolled as beta testers."
msgstr ""
"Bemærk : Brugerne skal have en aktiveret {platform_name} konto, før de kan "
"indskrives som betatestere."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:112
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"If this option is {em_start}checked{em_end}, users who have not enrolled in "
"your course will be automatically enrolled."
msgstr ""
"Hvis denne mulighed er {em_start}markeret {em_end} , vil brugere, der ikke "
"har tilmeldt sig dit kursus, automatisk blive tilmeldt."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:114
msgid "Checking this box has no effect if 'Remove beta testers' is selected."
msgstr ""
"Afkrydsning af dette felt har ingen effekt , hvis ' Fjern betatestere ' er "
"valgt."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:133
msgid "Add beta testers"
msgstr "Tilføj betatestere"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:134
msgid "Remove beta testers"
msgstr "Fjern betatestere"

#. Translators: an "Administration List" is a list, such as Course Staff, that
#. users can be added to.
#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:145
msgid "Course Team Management"
msgstr "Kursus Team Management"

#. Translators: an "Administrator Group" is a group, such as Course Staff,
#. that
#. users can be added to.
#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:151
msgid "Select a course team role:"
msgstr "Vælg en kursusteam rolle:"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:153
msgid "Getting available lists..."
msgstr "Hent tilgængelige lister ..."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:161
msgid ""
"Staff cannot modify these lists. To manage course team membership, a course "
"Admin must give you the Admin role to add Staff or Beta Testers, or the "
"Discussion Admin role to add discussion moderators and TAs."
msgstr ""
"Personalet kan ikke ændre disse lister. Hvis du vil administrere medlemmer "
"på et kursushold, skal et kursus Admin give dig tilladelse til at tilføje "
"personale eller beta-testere, eller adgang som Diskussionsadministrator for "
"at kunne tilføje diskussionsmoderatorer og TA'er ."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:172
msgid ""
"Course team members with the Staff role help you manage your course. Staff "
"can enroll and unenroll learners, as well as modify their grades and access "
"all course data. Staff also have access to your course in Studio and "
"Insights. Any users not yet enrolled in the course will be automatically "
"enrolled when added as Staff."
msgstr ""
"Kursesteammedlemmer med rollen Personale hjælper dig med at administrere dit"
" kursus. Personale kan tilmelde og framelde elever, samt ændre deres "
"karakterer og få adgang til alle kursusdata. Personale har også adgang til "
"dit kursus i Studio og Insights. Brugere, der endnu ikke er tilmeldt kurset,"
" vil blive tilmeldt automatisk, når de tilføjes som Personale."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:179
msgid "Add Staff"
msgstr "Tilføj personale"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:184
msgid "Limited Staff"
msgstr "Begrænset personale"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:186
msgid ""
"Course team members with the Limited Staff role help you manage your course."
" Limited Staff can enroll and unenroll learners, as well as modify their "
"grades and access all course data. Limited Staff don't have access to your "
"course in Studio. Any users not yet enrolled in the course will be "
"automatically enrolled when added as Limited Staff."
msgstr ""
"Kursesteammedlemmer med rollen Begrænset personale hjælper dig med at "
"administrere dit kursus. Begrænset personale kan tilmelde og framelde "
"elever, samt ændre deres karakterer og få adgang til alle kursusdata. "
"Begrænset personale har ikke adgang til dit kursus i Studio. Brugere, der "
"endnu ikke er tilmeldt kurset, vil blive tilmeldt automatisk, når de "
"tilføjes som Begrænset personale."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:193
msgid "Add Limited Staff"
msgstr "Tilføj begrænset personale"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:199
msgid "Admin"
msgstr "Administrator"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:201
msgid ""
"Course team members with the Admin role help you manage your course. They "
"can do all of the tasks that Staff can do, and can also add and remove the "
"Staff and Admin roles, discussion moderation roles, and the beta tester role"
" to manage course team membership. Any users not yet enrolled in the course "
"will be automatically enrolled when added as Admin."
msgstr ""
"Kursesteammedlemmer med rollen Administrator hjælper dig med at administrere"
" dit kursus. De kan udføre alle de opgaver, som Personale kan, og kan også "
"tilføje og fjerne rollerne Personale og Administrator, "
"diskussionsmoderatorroller og beta-testerrollen for at administrere "
"kursesteammedlemmer. Brugere, der endnu ikke er tilmeldt kurset, vil blive "
"tilmeldt automatisk, når de tilføjes som Administrator."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:208
msgid "Add Admin"
msgstr "Tilføj Admin"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:214
msgid "Beta Testers"
msgstr "Betatestere"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:216
msgid ""
"Beta Testers can see course content before other learners. They can make "
"sure that the content works, but have no additional privileges. Any users "
"not yet enrolled in the course will be automatically enrolled when added as "
"Beta Tester."
msgstr ""
"Beta-testere kan se kursusindholdet før andre elever. De kan sikre sig, at "
"indholdet fungerer, men har ingen yderligere privilegier. Brugere, der endnu"
" ikke er tilmeldt kurset, vil blive tilmeldt automatisk, når de tilføjes som"
" Beta-tester."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:222
msgid "Add Beta Tester"
msgstr "Tilføj betatestere"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:227
msgid "Discussion Admins"
msgstr "Diskussion Admin"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:229
msgid ""
"Discussion Admins can edit or delete any post, clear misuse flags, close and"
" re-open threads, endorse responses, and see posts from all groups. Their "
"posts are marked as 'staff'. They can also add and remove the discussion "
"moderation roles to manage course team membership. Any users not yet "
"enrolled in the course will be automatically enrolled when added as "
"Discussion Admin"
msgstr ""
"Diskussionsadministratorer kan redigere eller slette ethvert indlæg, rydde "
"misbrugsflag, lukke og genåbne tråde, godkende svar og se indlæg fra alle "
"grupper. Deres indlæg er markeret som 'personale'. De kan også tilføje og "
"fjerne diskussionsmoderatorroller for at administrere kursesteammedlemmer. "
"Brugere, der endnu ikke er tilmeldt kurset, vil blive tilmeldt automatisk, "
"når de tilføjes som Diskussionsadministrator."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:237
msgid "Add Discussion Admin"
msgstr "Tilføj Diskussion Admin"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:242
msgid "Course Data Researcher"
msgstr "Kursus Dataforsker"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:244
msgid ""
"Course Data Researchers can access the data download tab. Any users not yet "
"enrolled in the course will be automatically enrolled when added as Course "
"Data Researcher."
msgstr ""
"Kursusdataforskere kan få adgang til fanen for datanedlastning. Brugere, der"
" endnu ikke er tilmeldt kurset, vil blive tilmeldt automatisk, når de "
"tilføjes som Kursusdataforsker."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:248
msgid "Add Course Data Researcher"
msgstr "Tilføj kursusdataforsker"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:256
msgid "Discussion Moderators"
msgstr "Diskussionsmoderatorer"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:258
msgid ""
"Discussion Moderators can edit or delete any post, clear misuse flags, close"
" and re-open threads, endorse responses, and see posts from all groups. "
"Their posts are marked as 'staff'. They cannot manage course team membership"
" by adding or removing discussion moderation roles. Any users not yet "
"enrolled in the course will be automatically enrolled when added as "
"Discussion Moderator"
msgstr ""
"Diskussionsmoderatorer kan redigere eller slette ethvert indlæg, rydde "
"misbrugsflag, lukke og genåbne tråde, godkende svar og se indlæg fra alle "
"grupper. Deres indlæg er markeret som 'personale'. De kan ikke administrere "
"kursesteammedlemmer ved at tilføje eller fjerne diskussionsmoderatorroller. "
"Brugere, der endnu ikke er tilmeldt kurset, vil blive tilmeldt automatisk, "
"når de tilføjes som Diskussionsmoderator."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:265
msgid "Add Moderator"
msgstr "Tilføj moderator"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:270
msgid "Group Community TA"
msgstr "Gruppefællesskab TA"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:272
msgid ""
"Group Community TAs are members of the community who help course teams "
"moderate discussions. Group Community TAs see only posts by learners in "
"their assigned group. They can edit or delete posts, clear flags, close and "
"re-open threads, and endorse responses, but only for posts by learners in "
"their group. Their posts are marked as 'Community TA'. Any users not yet "
"enrolled in the course will be automatically enrolled when added as Group "
"Community TA"
msgstr ""
"Gruppe Community TAs er medlemmer af fællesskabet, der hjælper kursesteams "
"med at moderere diskussioner. Gruppe Community TAs ser kun indlæg fra elever"
" i deres tildelte gruppe. De kan redigere eller slette indlæg, rydde flag, "
"lukke og genåbne tråde og godkende svar, men kun for indlæg fra elever i "
"deres gruppe. Deres indlæg er markeret som 'Community TA'. Brugere, der "
"endnu ikke er tilmeldt kurset, vil blive tilmeldt automatisk, når de "
"tilføjes som Gruppe Community TA."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:279
msgid "Add Group Community TA"
msgstr "Tilføj gruppefællesskab TA"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:286
msgid ""
"Community TAs are members of the community who help course teams moderate "
"discussions. They can see posts by learners in their assigned cohort or "
"enrollment track, and can edit or delete posts, clear flags, close or re-"
"open threads, and endorse responses. Their posts are marked as 'Community "
"TA'. Any users not yet enrolled in the course will be automatically enrolled"
" when added as Community TA"
msgstr ""
"Community TAs er medlemmer af fællesskabet, der hjælper kursesteams med at "
"moderere diskussioner. De kan se indlæg fra elever i deres tildelte cohorte "
"eller tilmeldingsspor og kan redigere eller slette indlæg, rydde flag, lukke"
" eller genåbne tråde og godkende svar. Deres indlæg er markeret som "
"'Community TA'. Brugere, der endnu ikke er tilmeldt kurset, vil blive "
"tilmeldt automatisk, når de tilføjes som Community TA."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:292
msgid "Add Community TA"
msgstr "Tilføj Fællesskabs-TA"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:299
msgid "CCX Coaches"
msgstr "CCX-trænere"

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:301
msgid ""
"CCX Coaches are able to create their own Custom Courses based on this "
"course, which they can use to provide personalized instruction to their own "
"students based in this course material."
msgstr ""
"CCX Coaches kan danne deres egne brugerdefinerede Kurser baseret på dette "
"kursus, som de kan bruge til at yde personlig instruktion til deres egne "
"studerende baseret på dette kursusmateriale."

#: lms/templates/instructor/instructor_dashboard_2/membership.html:306
msgid "Add CCX Coach"
msgstr "Tilføj CCX Coach"

